examples.en: The fog reduced visibility to a quarter of a mile.
Visibility was bad due to low cloud.
All planes were grounded because of poor visibility.
The exhibition helped increase the visibility of women artists.
The extra publicity helped to increase the company's visibility.
The search for survivors was abandoned because of poor visibility.
Visibility on the roads is down to 20 metres due to heavy fog.
We ran into a big rainstorm on Highway 6, and the visibility was so poor we had to pull over.
